0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 613.00 Tm
(target likely business customers.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 597.00 Tm
(Call Detail Data \(CDD\) contains metadata about calls, such as the numbers involved, time of) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 583.00 Tm
