(1. Customer Churn and Survival Analysis) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 685.00 Tm
(Customer churn happens when a customer stops using a product or service. If someone cancels) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 671.00 Tm
(a subscription or becomes inactive, that customer has churned.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 655.00 Tm
(Survival analysis studies the time until an event occurs. In marketing and customer) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 641.00 Tm
(management, the event is often churn. Instead of looking only at who left, survival analysis) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 627.00 Tm
(also looks at when they left.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 611.00 Tm
(Customer tenure is the length of time a customer stays with the company. Higher tenure) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 597.00 Tm
(usually means greater long-term value.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 581.00 Tm
(The half-life period is the time by which 50% of customers have churned. A short half-life) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 567.00 Tm
(suggests weak retention.) Tj
ET
BT
0.145 0.388 0.655 rg
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 545.00 Tm
(2. Why Retention Matters) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 528.00 Tm
(Companies spend money to acquire customers. If customers leave quickly, the firm may not) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 514.00 Tm
(recover that cost. This is why retention is often more profitable than constantly acquiring) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 500.00 Tm
(new customers.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 484.00 Tm
(A small reduction in churn can lead to a large increase in profit because loyal customers) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 470.00 Tm
(tend to buy more over time, cost less to serve, and may bring referrals.) Tj
